metadata.description: Mind Monks is an exclusive community of 888 Monks, each on their journey towards living their best life, collectively challenging the status quo. A Genesis Mind Monks NFT will grant you exclusive access to our global retreat centers (IRL), where you can safely indulge in plant medicine and natural healing practices, facilitated by the world's best spiritual teachers. Check out our comprehensive whitepaper for all project details.
